                        Meram/Konya
                    </a>
                </small>
                <small class="me-3">
                    <i class="fas fa-envelope me-2 text-secondary"></i><a href="#" class="text-white">uresinlerkuyumculuk@gmail.com</a>
                </small>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="container px-0">
